testbed.db
Class LogMessage

java.lang.Object
  testbed.db.LogMessage

public class LogMessage
extends java.lang.Object

This class holds information about a message passed between a pair of agents, to be displayed in a TransactionLog.

Author:
K. Fullam and G. Muller
